{"tid":210790,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"天氣報告同打茄輪有咩關係?","createTime":"2017-04-21T07:59:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-21T15:31:16.000Z","uid":29627,"like":88,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ab7286cf6c4bd9cda1d78b33cde48c8ec8f6de2e","tid":210790,"uid":29627,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T07:59:31.000Z","msg":"【15:20 更新】現時氣溫27.7&deg;C，相對濕度86%。黃色暴雨警告信號現正生效。雷暴警告亦生效，有效時間至今日下午5時正，預料香港有幾陣狂風雷暴。預料高達每小時80公里或以上的陣風吹襲香港。<br />\n<br />\n天文台發出特別天氣提示，一道強雷雨帶正橫過珠江口，預料未來一兩小時本港會有大驟雨及狂風雷暴。市民應提高警惕。<br />\n<br />\n位於廣東北部的一道冷鋒正逐漸向南移動，其相關的雷雨正影響廣東。<br />\n<br />\n預測今日多雲，有驟雨及幾陣狂風雷暴，初時雨勢頗大。吹和緩至清勁南風，今晚轉吹偏北風，氣溫顯著下降，會由日間的29&deg;C跌至今晚的22&deg;C，明日清晨更只有約19&deg;C。<br />\n<br />\n展望明早天氣較涼，日間部分時間天色明朗。下周初大致多雲。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170421/large/1492759851_098f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170421%2Flarge%2F1492759851_098f.jpg&h=9d997a4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n預測今日多雲，有驟雨及幾陣狂風雷暴，初時雨勢頗大。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170421/56592515\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170421%2F56592515&d=nqzd6QM3TLyrPp4uhCfCny7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=07849f2a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170421%2F56592515&h=12de3884\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170421/56592515</a>"},{"pid":"c454cb56aec7f1127dcfe0917a8b71cb574d7827","tid":210790,"uid":82398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T08:07:53.000Z","msg":"生死離別"},{"pid":"1591228505bd37fb25d52292c2b9626a2cac46b6","tid":210790,"uid":62085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T08:08:51.000Z","msg":"我都見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15cf44618ee56195f99b304d9ba